Me:      I'm LFG if you could use an enchanter?<br>
Someone: Oh, we're full.<br>
Me:      Grr.<br>
<br>
I'd almost always rather hunt in a decent group than solo, since I think grouping is what makes EQ fun.  But a few conversations like the above make it hard for me to sympathize with people who are angry that enchanters can solo.<br>
